'''Roman Patrick Banks''' (born October 23, 1969) is a former American basketball coach and the current athletic director at [[Southern University]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Johnson |first=Luke |url=http://www.theadvocate.com/baton_rouge/sports/southern/article_1140a590-1647-11e7-b2ec-cb7c61a25bca.html |title=Southern's Roman Banks named Jaguars' long-term athletic director; Morris Scott named interim basketball coach |date=2017-03-31 |accessdate=2017-04-10}}</ref> Banks previously served as the [[Southern Jaguars basketball|head men's basketball coach]] for the [[Southern Jaguars]] before he was promoted to AD on March 31, 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gojagsports.com/ViewArticle.dbml?SPSID=641851&SPID=96916&DB_LANG=C&DB_OEM_ID=28100&ATCLID=205348958&Q_SEASON=2013|title=Roman Banks Bio - Official Site of the Southern University Jaguars |accessdate=2017-04-10}}</ref>

